{"tid":986483,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"[三十歲女教練] 男足女教練豪言 用下體大小定正選!!","createTime":"2019-01-18T13:15:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-18T17:58:58.000Z","uid":34571,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"8bec859d167bc3ec60fc02aecbd3444bb4477a5b","tid":986483,"uid":34571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-18T13:15:27.000Z","msg":"「大台」一套剛大結局的劇集，主角有一句口頭禪叫「誰大誰惡誰正確」，想不到在德國球壇中，竟有一位女教練以近似的準則決定正選陣容，利用球員下體陰莖的大小決定出場次序！<br />\n<br />\n現年 30 歲的 Imke W&uuml;bbenhorst 是德國第五級聯賽球隊 Cloppenburg 的領隊，她日前接受傳媒訪問時，有記者問到當 Imke W&uuml;bbenhorst 進入更衣室時，球員是否全部穿好球衣，這位女漢子竟然豪言球員無需特意穿好衣服，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">並補充指自己十分專業，會按照他們陰莖的大小來決定正選陣容，十分誇張。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n雖然不知道 Imke W&uuml;bbenhorst 是否真的「誰大誰長誰正選」作為排陣準則，不過這位曾經效力過 Cloppenburg 女子隊，並曾入選德國 U 23 女足的前球員，<span style=\"color: red;\">作為德國首五級聯賽中，唯一一名女性教練，帶隊的成績可謂令人失望，現時球隊是包尾大幡</span>，相信 Imke W&uuml;bbenhorst 要用心分析和比較球員的優劣，帶領球隊逃出降班區。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"38d6e362cb6b3d439ed7c3feff933f1b5e496b9e","tid":986483,"uid":205462,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-18T13:18:02.000Z","msg":"難怪排榜尾，原來班球員每場未出更衣室已經射到腳軟<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"318448a85b4e9b1fb433853b0d618e044e37315d","tid":986483,"uid":43493,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-18T13:19:07.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/692298914179660/posts/1997146143694924/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F692298914179660%2Fposts%2F1997146143694924%2F&d=Ufld9kdgf6plUZmBe%2FWzNp4f2li5K%2Fs6EGgmwhpeblA%3D&h=d8f27cca\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/692298914179660/posts/1997146143694924/</a><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nFake news"},{"pid":"47e21bb00c933ace8b68ca6fec5bc7918678ea7c","tid":986483,"uid":12113